<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣١ - <span class="c2">(وأرضٍ قَدْ قطعْتُ بهَا الهَوَاهِي ... مِنْ الجِنَّانِ سَربَخُهَا مَلِيعُ)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
